### Step 5: Evaluate and promote

After RLCR completes:

1. Validate correctness on all workloads:
```bash
gpu-run.sh uv run --project /mnt/public/zhaotianlang/projects/kernel-agent/sol-execbench scripts/run_dataset.py problem/ --solution-name candidates/candidate_NNN.py -o outputs/traces --timeout 120
```

2. Benchmark performance:
```bash
gpu-run.sh uv run --project /mnt/public/zhaotianlang/projects/kernel-agent/sol-execbench scripts/run_dataset.py problem/ --solution-name candidates/candidate_NNN.py -o outputs/traces --timeout 300 --iterations 50
```

3. Compare against current best (`{{CURRENT_BEST_CANDIDATE}}`):
   - Must pass correctness on all workloads
   - Must be faster than `{{CURRENT_BEST_CANDIDATE}}` on at least half the workloads without regressing the rest

4. If better, promote:
```bash
cp candidates/candidate_NNN.py solution.py
```

5. Update `status.json` with new best candidate and speedup.

6. If more improvement is possible, loop back to Phase 2 with a new draft.
